          "filename": "vo-100-professor-ichistrasz-09-m",
          "fileDataId": 4689624,
          "audioUrl": "https://wow.zamimg.com/sound-ids/live/enus/216/4689624/VO_100_Professor_Ichistrasz_09_M.ogg",
          "text": "Me?! There is too much nature! What are you doing?",
          "status": "accepted",
          "selected": false,
          "notes": ""
        },
        {
          "soundId": 208114,
          "filename": "vo-100-professor-ichistrasz-08-m",
          "fileDataId": 4689619,
          "audioUrl": "https://wow.zamimg.com/sound-ids/live/enus/211/4689619/VO_100_Professor_Ichistrasz_08_M.ogg",
          "text": "Well, it seems like things are in further disrepair than we anticipated.",
          "status": "pending",
          "selected": false,
          "notes": ""
        },
        {
          "soundId": 208099,
          "filename": "vo-100-professor-ichistrasz-04-m",
          "fileDataId": 4689576,
          "audioUrl": "https://wow.zamimg.com/sound-ids/live/enus/168/4689576/VO_100_Professor_Ichistrasz_04_M.ogg",
          "text": "What an overgrown statement.",
          "status": "pending",
          "selected": false,
          "notes": ""
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 189668,
      "name": "Professor Maxdormu",
      "elite": true,
      "quotes": [
        {
          "soundId": 204573,
          "filename": "vo-100-professor-maxdormu-06-m",
          "fileDataId": 4673148,
          "audioUrl": "https://wow.zamimg.com/sound-ids/live/enus/124/4673148/VO_100_Professor_Maxdormu_06_M.ogg",
          "text": "Ah! Here we are! Ahem--long ago, members of the blue dragonflight accidentally overloaded an arcane elemental and created a powerful construct named Vexamus that quickly started to wreak havoc!",
          "status": "accepted",
          "selected": false,
          "notes": ""
        },
        {
          "soundId": 204583,
          "filename": "vo-100-professor-maxdormu-16-m",
          "fileDataId": 4673158,
          "audioUrl": "https://wow.zamimg.com/sound-ids/live/enus/134/4673158/VO_100_Professor_Maxdormu_16_M.ogg",
          "text": "Please excuse the mess! It has been quite some time since students have been here. I am just putting together my lesson plan.",
          "status": "pending",
          "selected": false,
          "notes": ""
        },
        {
          "soundId": 204575,
          "filename": "vo-100-professor-maxdormu-08-m",
          "fileDataId": 4673150,
          "audioUrl": "https://wow.zamimg.com/sound-ids/live/enus/126/4673150/VO_100_Professor_Maxdormu_08_M.ogg",
          "text": "Since you did so well on your lesson, feel free to take something from the 'Good Students' Reward Chest.",
          "status": "pending",
          "selected": false,
          "notes": ""
        },
        {
          "soundId": 204574,
          "filename": "vo-100-professor-maxdormu-07-m",
          "fileDataId": 4673149,
          "audioUrl": "https://wow.zamimg.com/sound-ids/live/enus/125/4673149/VO_100_Professor_Maxdormu_07_M.ogg",
          "text": "Though Vexamus tried its best to defeat the dragons, it was ultimately destroyed. Well done!",
          "status": "pending",
          "selected": false,
          "notes": ""
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 187287,
      "name": "Professor Mystakria",
      "elite": true,
